querys.name: SalesPerProductQueryAdv
querys.expression:
SELECT SUM(ol.totalWithVat) AS ammount, ol.product, p._name
FROM vw_SaleOrder_Lines ol
INNER JOIN vw_Product p ON p._code=ol.product
GROUP BY ol.product, p._name
ORDER BY ammount DESC

querys.name: QuarterSalesQueryAdv
querys.expression:
SELECT DATE_PART('quarter', om._date) AS quarter, SUM(om.totalWithVat) AS ammount
FROM vw_SaleOrder om
WHERE DATE_PART('year', om._date) = cast(@year as double precision)
GROUP BY DATE_PART('quarter', om._date)
ORDER BY DATE_PART('quarter', om._date)

querys.name: MonthlySalesQueryAdv
querys.expression:
SELECT DATE_PART('month', om._date) AS month, SUM(om.totalWithVat) AS ammount
FROM vw_SaleOrder om
WHERE DATE_PART('year', om._date) = cast(@year as double precision)
GROUP BY DATE_PART('month', om._date)
ORDER BY DATE_PART('month', om._date)

querys.name: SalesPerSalesPersonQueryAdv
querys.expression:
SELECT SUM(om.totalWithVat) AS ammount, om.salesPerson, sp._name
FROM vw_SaleOrder om
INNER JOIN vw_SalesPerson sp ON sp._code=om.salesPerson
GROUP BY om.salesPerson, sp._name
ORDER BY ammount DESC

querys.name: SalesPerClientQueryAdv
querys.expression:
SELECT SUM(om.totalWithVat) AS ammount, om.client, c._name
FROM vw_SaleOrder om
INNER JOIN vw_Client c ON c._code=om.client
GROUP BY om.client, c._name
ORDER BY ammount DESC
